General.Name: Vista Group International Ltd
General.Description: Vista Group International Limited provides software and data analytics solutions to the film industry worldwide. It operates through three segments: Cinema, Movio, and Additional Group Companies. The company offers Vista Cinema, a cinema management software; and Veezi, a cloud-based software for the independent cinema market. It also provides Movio, a cloud-based solution that offers marketing data analytics and campaign management solutions; Numero, a box office reporting platform for film distributors and cinemas; and MACCS, a software solution that manages the distribution of movies to cinemas. In addition, the company offers Flicks, a movie, cinema, and streaming guide; and Powster, a g film marketing product that enables consumers to discover cinema showtimes on official movie websites. Further, it provides software licensing; Web platform licensing; and data analytics, and marketing services. The company was founded in 1996 and is based in Auckland, New Zealand.
